node.text:
Congratulations @gtankenman for closing your first deal for a fat check of $25,000! Excited to see you get more bro 🔥

I always preach to my students — if the numbers don’t work to fit a rental property or flip - just wholesale it, get your money and find another deal. And that’s what Andrew is doing. Let’s goooo

Learn more about Mentorship by tapping the link in my bio 🔥

#realestate #realestateinvesting #realestateinvestor #wholesalerealestate

node.text:
Congratulations @theteapham for finding your first deal within 90 days of being in the program! Tiffany was accountant for 10 years and always wanted to go into real estate since she purchased her first primary property in 2017. She mentioned she didn’t have any guidance and held herself back for a while until covid. She decided to take the jump into real estate and quit her job at the end of Jan 2021.

Want to be mentored by me? Link in bio to sign up.

#realestate #realestateinvesting #realestateinvestor #wealth #wealthbuilding #realestatetips #wholesalerealestate

node.title: Student Makes $15,000 From Her First Wholesale Deal In 90 Days

node.text:
I’m on a mission to help the low income community that I grew up in - NewHolly, Seattle by raising funds to build a brand new soccer field and supportive programs and resources for the community with my friends at @ravefound & @soundersfc.

Here’s what you’ll get when you donate these amounts:

➡️ $10,000 Donation: Group Hangout with Thach For A Day (2 Group separate sessions of 10 People - Limited to 20 People)
1. Create a Personalized Road Map To Wealth ($5000)
2. Tour Thach’s Real Estate Projects($2000)
3. Meet The Team and Q&A ($1500)
4. Pick Thach’s Brain - Q&A ($7500)
5. Goodie Bag - New Merch ($500)
6. Ride In The BRRRR Machine

➡️ $20,000 Donation: 1-on-1 with Thach For A Day (Limited to 10 People)
*Everything In the $10K Donation PLUS*
7. Wholesale Mentorship Course ($2,000)
8. 2 Weekly Jumpstart Coaching Calls Live For 1 Year ($2400 value) - *not 6 months*
9. Spend Time with Thach Personally 1-on-1 for One Day And Ride In The BRRRR Machine ($15,000 value /Priceless)

LINK IN BIO!!! (side note: any amount of donation helps as well)

node.title: How To Get 1-on-1 Mentorship From Thach Nguyen

node.text:
Congratulations @theteapham for finding your first deal within 90 days of being in the program! Tiffany was accountant for 10 years and always wanted to go into real estate since she purchased her first primary property in 2017. She mentioned she didn’t have any guidance and held herself back for a while until covid. She decided to take the jump into real estate and quit her job at the end of Jan 2021.

Want to be mentored by me? Link in bio to sign up.

#realestate #realestateinvesting #realestateinvestor #wealth #wealthbuilding #realestatetips #wholesalerealestate

I’m on a mission to help the low income community that I grew up in - NewHolly, Seattle by raising funds to build a brand new soccer field and supportive programs and resources for the community with my friends at @ravefound & @soundersfc.

Here’s what you’ll get when you donate these amounts:

➡️ $10,000 Donation: Group Hangout with Thach For A Day (2 Group separate sessions of 10 People - Limited to 20 People)
1. Create a Personalized Road Map To Wealth ($5000)
2. Tour Thach’s Real Estate Projects($2000)
3. Meet The Team and Q&A ($1500)
4. Pick Thach’s Brain - Q&A ($7500)
5. Goodie Bag - New Merch ($500)
6. Ride In The BRRRR Machine

➡️ $20,000 Donation: 1-on-1 with Thach For A Day (Limited to 10 People)
*Everything In the $10K Donation PLUS*
7. Wholesale Mentorship Course ($2,000)
8. 2 Weekly Jumpstart Coaching Calls Live For 1 Year ($2400 value) - *not 6 months*
9. Spend Time with Thach Personally 1-on-1 for One Day And Ride In The BRRRR Machine ($15,000 value /Priceless)

LINK IN BIO!!! (side note: any amount of donation helps as well)
